🔴 **Tool Issue** — `arm-horizondb-models-node.api.md:337-338`
```ts
export interface PrivateEndpointConnectionResource extends Resource {
    properties?: PrivateEndpointConnectionProperties;
}
```
`PrivateEndpointConnectionResource` and `PrivateEndpointConnection` (line 321) are structurally identical — both extend `Resource` with `properties?: PrivateEndpointConnectionProperties`. This duplication typically indicates two different Swagger models that should be merged.

**Fix:** Merge the duplicated models in the spec repo or use `@clientName` to unify them into a single type, then trigger SDK regeneration. Also report in the [generation tool repository](https://github.com/Azure/autorest.typescript/issues).
